fetter.detail: A traveler from another world who had their only kin taken away, forcing them to embark on a journey to find The Seven.

0.name: Normal Attack: Foreign Rockblade
0.description:
<color=#FFD780FF>Normal Attack</color>
Performs up to 5 rapid strikes.

<color=#FFD780FF>Charged Attack</color>
Consumes a certain amount of Stamina to unleash 2 rapid sword strikes.

<color=#FFD780FF>Plunging Attack</color>
Plunges from mid-air to strike the ground below, damaging opponents along the path and dealing AoE DMG upon impact.

1.name: Starfell Sword
1.description: You disgorge a meteorite from the depths of the earth, dealing AoE Geo DMG. The meteorite is considered a Geo Construct, and can be climbed or used to block attacks. Hold This skill's positioning may be adjusted. You spoke with Paimon about the final destination of falling stars.

3.name: Wake of Earth
3.description: Energizing the Geo deep underground, you set off expanding shockwaves. Launches surrounding opponents back and deals AoE Geo DMG. A stone wall is erected at the edges of the shockwave. The stone wall is considered a Geo Construct, and may be used to block attacks. You and Paimon studied the pulse of the mountains.

5.name: Frenzied Rockslide
5.description: The final hit of a Normal Attack combo triggers a collapse, dealing 60% of ATK as <color=#FFE699FF>AoE Geo DMG</color>.

0.name: Invincible Stonewall
0.description: Party members within the radius of <color=#FFD780FF>Wake of Earth</color> have their CRIT Rate increased by 10% and have increased resistance against interruption.

1.name: Rockcore Meltdown
1.description: When the meteorite created by <color=#FFD780FF>Starfell Sword</color> is destroyed, it will also explode, dealing additional <color=#FFE699FF>AoE Geo DMG</color> equal to the amount of damage dealt by Starfell Sword.

2.name: Will of the Rock
2.description: Increases the Level of <color=#FFD780FF>Wake of Earth</color> by 3.\nMaximum upgrade level is 15.

3.name: Reaction Force
3.description: The shockwave triggered by <color=#FFD780FF>Wake of Earth</color> regenerates 5 Energy for every opponent hit.\nA maximum of 25 Energy can be regenerated in this manner at any one time.

4.name: Meteorite Impact
4.description: Increases the Level of <color=#FFD780FF>Starfell Sword</color> by 3.\nMaximum upgrade level is 15.

5.name: Everlasting Boulder
5.description: The barrier created by <color=#FFD780FF>Wake of Earth</color> lasts 5s longer.\nThe meteorite created by <color=#FFD780FF>Starfell Sword</color> lasts 10s longer.
